<h3 style="margin:1em 0 0;">How does it work?</h3>
<p style="margin: 0 0 1em;">
	<ul>
		<li>You submit your project</li>
		<li>We review it</li> 
		<li>If approved, it gets sent to a private group of top talent</li> 
		<li>This group shares your project with their network and you get responses within days (if not hours).</li>
	</ul>
It's a quick, authentic way to make real connections with the top talent in the design and development industry. But it's not for everyone. You gotta be self-funded, profitable, and have a quality project to submit.</p>

<h3 style="margin:1em 0 0;">So is this a job board?</h3>
<p style="margin: 0 0 1em;">No. This is a little different. We're not going to plaster your project around in hopes you find a needle in the hayspam. Instead freelancers and influencers that are trusted in the industry will receive your project via a single targeted email. These well-connected freelancers and influencers will then either reply to you directly or send your project to someone they know and is perfect for the project.
</p>

<h3 style="margin:1em 0 0;">How much does it cost?</h3>
<p style="margin: 0 0 1em;">Several companies (like Dropbox, Airbnb, Square and more) have built $1,000,000+ teams and used Folyo in the past. You can post a project for just a $299 one-time fee. If we deny your project or you're not 100% satisfied, you'll get a refund no questions asked.</p>

<h3 style="margin:1em 0 0;">How long does it take?</h3>
<p style="margin: 0 0 1em;">If you're in a huge rush this probably isn't for you. We slow down the process on purpose because it helps you make a great choice and minimize risk for all parties. That said, you'll probably need about 7-10 days total to use Folyo. It takes 15 minutes to fill out the initial project form. Then up to 24 hours to be approved and get your project sent out. From there it can take a couple days to a few weeks to finish interviewing and talking with candidates.</p>

<h3 style="margin:1em 0 0;">Who sees my project?</h3>
<p style="margin: 0 0 1em;">Literally the nicest, smartest people in the world. We hand-pick people who have amazing audiences, networks, and knowledge about your specific type of project so we send you to the best.</p>

<h3 style="margin:1em 0 0;">What happens if I don't find someone?</h3>
<p style="margin: 0 0 1em;">You're entitled to a full refund. Zero risk.</p>

<h3 style="margin:1em 0 0;">What if my budget is under $1K?</h3>
<p style="margin: 0 0 1em;">Sorry. Folyo is only for projects that have a monthly budget of $1,000 or higher. We believe in doing work that's valuable to a business. </p>

